            <description>• Added a scale effect when dragging cards
• Cards can now be automatically moved to (other) tableau stacks, preferring the largest stack
• The whole tableau stacks are now used as drop zones for cards and card fans
• Secondary clicks (right mouse button clicks) can now be used to automatically move cards


• Cards that are not the top-most card in the waste pile or in foundation stacks can not be dragged anymore
• Improved animations when undoing and redoing moves
						</description>
